                            <comment id="13184559" author="hwellmann.de" created="Thu, 31 Mar 2016 08:14:39 -0400"  >&lt;p&gt;The root cause seems to be in &lt;tt&gt;JAXRSArchiveImpl.addGeneratedApplication()&lt;/tt&gt;. This block&lt;/p&gt;

